  "detailed_description": "Become a wizard who must find a way out of a dungeon filled with hordes of enemies. Cast spells, dodge enemy attacks, and gather loot to upgrade your character.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/c98853bf8fcff66454d4650705d806f5.poster.avif?t=1741708840\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/c98853bf8fcff66454d4650705d806f5.webm?t=1741708840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/c98853bf8fcff66454d4650705d806f5.mp4?t=1741708840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHOOSE WISELY</h2>Each run presents many choices to test your strategic thinking. Which element of spells should you focus on? How are you going to survive the final floor? How much risk are you willing to take?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/a3f91a92b7689d4e78830ad4d7286519.poster.avif?t=1741708840\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/a3f91a92b7689d4e78830ad4d7286519.webm?t=1741708840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/a3f91a92b7689d4e78830ad4d7286519.mp4?t=1741708840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VARIETY & REPLAYABILITY</h2>Chaos Caster was carefully crafted to maximize replay value. Every mechanic was designed to increase playstyle variety and ensure that no two runs are the same.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/7b973750026af565071a988e9178f40e.poster.avif?t=1741708840\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/7b973750026af565071a988e9178f40e.webm?t=1741708840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/7b973750026af565071a988e9178f40e.mp4?t=1741708840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
